    "name": "Savor the Sting",
    "permission": {
        "default": 0
    },
    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You inflict pain upon the target and revel in their anguish. This deals 1d4 mental damage and 1d4 persistent mental damage; the target must attempt a Will save. As long as the target is taking @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} from this spell, you gain a +1 status bonus to attack rolls and skill checks against the target.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The target is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The target takes half damage and no @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage}.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The target takes full initial and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage}.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  The target takes double initial and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage}.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (+1)</b>  The initial damage increases by 1d4 and the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} increases by 1d4.</p>",
